HEADWORD: Extersion
<hw>Ex*ter"sion</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[L.
<ets>extergere</ets>, <ets>extersum</ets>, to wipe out; <ets>ex</ets>
out + <ets>tergere</ets> to wipe or rub off.]</ety> <def>The act of
